{"tid":900531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"默克爾被錯認成馬克龍夫人 急忙澄清：我是德國總理","createTime":"2018-11-13T09:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T12:04:51.000Z","uid":32938,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2daf40b10d22bef83b4692c392a55e60a19f6417","tid":900531,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/news/crawl/20/w550h270/20181112/NGJM-hnstwwr1835758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fnews%2Fcrawl%2F20%2Fw550h270%2F20181112%2FNGJM-hnstwwr1835758.jpg&h=e4b0337d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國總理默克爾與法國總統馬克龍共同出席位於法國瓦茲省（Oise）的第一次世界大戰停戰百年紀念活動。<br />\n<br />\n在與當地民眾交流時，一位101歲老人錯將站在馬克龍身邊的德國總理默克爾誤認成了馬克龍夫人，默克爾哭笑不得，急忙用法語解釋自己是德國總理。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍先生，這太不可思議了，我能夠與共和國總統握手，這太棒了&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n這位老人在與馬克龍握手時興奮地說道，接著她轉向站在馬克龍身邊的默克爾詢問，&ldquo;您是馬克龍夫人吧&rdquo;，默克爾隨即向她用法語解釋：&ldquo;我是德國總理&rdquo;，雖然反復了兩次，但是老人似乎沒有聽清，依舊高興地重複道：&ldquo;這太棒了！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"691612271e6b49c693b4ee0e476953e86d853636","tid":900531,"uid":56467,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"阿婆都feel到馬膠龍鍾意驅風"},{"pid":"a948346a69288c9f2d654f28deee353efa830bc8","tid":900531,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bdbd984830870e74cf57bebf8b3f036f4faa9a","tid":900531,"uid":199145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"691612271e6b49c693b4ee0e476953e86d853636","tid":900531,"uid":56467,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"阿婆都feel到馬膠龍鍾意驅風"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"全國都知馬卡龍愛驅風<br />\n阿婆：今次仲唔輪到我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb423dcc34ea209cb82dbb19c130a98b7fcf068","tid":900531,"uid":202348,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:13